name: Alexei Rusu
bio: As a full-stack web developer with a background in choreography, I bring a unique perspective to the development process. My combination of technical expertise and creative vision, honed by my choreographic education, allows me to approach problem-solving and design from a holistic perspective.  I am a team player, looking to integrate technical and artistic elements to create intuitive and visually engaging user experiences that inspire and connect with users. Always eager to learn and grow in the exciting field of development.
